# Run Project After Done

After completing implementation or feature work on ChaseQuiz, always run the project so the user can test it.

## Commands

Start both backend and frontend in the background:

1. **Backend** (port 5000):
   ```
   cd c:\Users\User\Desktop\ChaseQuiz\backend; npm run dev
   ```

2. **Frontend** (port 5173):
   ```
   cd c:\Users\User\Desktop\ChaseQuiz\frontend; npm run dev
   ```

Run both as background tasks. Tell the user when they're ready and provide the URL: http://localhost:5173
